      • actionRefine

        private void actionRefine()
        Called when the refine button is pressed. Filters the searched data and keeps the items with their titles containing the keyword typed in the text area.

      • actionAbout

        private void actionAbout()
        Called when the about your team button is pressed. Makes a dialog displaying information about the team members appear.

      • actionLast

        private void actionLast()
        Called when the last search button is pressed. Reverts the search results to the previous search.

      • actionQuit

        private void actionQuit()
        Called when the quit button is pressed. Exits the program and closes all connections.

      • actionClose

        private void actionClose()
        Called when the close button is pressed. Clears the current search record and initialize all tabs to their initial state.
